bottom; padding: 2px 8px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(142, 201, 101);">课程安排</section><section style="border: 1px solid rgb(142, 201, 101); margin-top: -1.86em; padding: 2em 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="padding: 5px;">人无礼不立，该章节涉及课程有：</p><p style="padding: 5px;">1、着装礼仪；&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 5px;">&nbsp;2、乘车礼仪；</p><p style="padding: 5px;">&nbsp;3、电梯礼仪；</p><p style="padding: 5px;">4、中餐礼仪；</p><p style="padding: 5px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;5、西餐礼仪；&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 5px;">&nbsp;6、站坐行礼仪；</p><p style="padding: 5px;">7、引领礼仪； &nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 5px;">8、拜访礼仪；</p><p style="padding: 5px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;9、名片礼仪等。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section>

